{"tid":1452944,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我系P牌仔，非常把抱歉","createTime":"2019-08-12T02:50:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T02:54:57.000Z","uid":267680,"like":3,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f28744c9b741fb34c36f5399a1af4531859dbe9d","tid":1452944,"uid":267680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T02:50:13.000Z","msg":"我認我系之前既事件真系跟錯左風向<br />\n叫大家唔好使用暴力<br />\n但原來暴力都系來源自假冒既黑警<br />\n<br />\n我想講聲 「對唔住，我願意撒回之前既言論。」<br />\n<br />\n另外，請蓮燈神封鎖P牌及6月9後申請的P牌帳號<br />\n避免再有同樣事情發生<br />\n<br />\n#風向唔應該由了解唔夠深既P牌去發言<br />\n#香港移民都要7年先有投票權<br />\n<br />\n我正式宣布<br />\n從今日起 放核彈都唔割蓆<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f99ea5250e138d69ce2cdf9ecdf319366753f2e","tid":1452944,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T02:52:01.000Z","msg":"系<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c06594f6cbf5fc32d5c3dd596f228e18566e8ca","tid":1452944,"uid":267680,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3f99ea5250e138d69ce2cdf9ecdf319366753f2e","tid":1452944,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T02:52:01.000Z","msg":"系<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T02:52:57.000Z","msg":"更正： 無個把字"},{"pid":"e291aae49329bb34d3b4064bd84825e19d5db565","tid":1452944,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T02:54:57.000Z","msg":"系<br />\n撒"}]}